‚ćĚ Fastify-style HTTP router for Dyalog APL, built on top of Jarvis.
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Usage:
‚ćĚ   ‚ćĚ First define your functions, ListUsers, and GetUser, and CreateUser
‚ćĚ   router‚ÜźStark.New ()
‚ćĚ   ‚ćĚ Matrix mode (method path handler options per row):
‚ćĚ   router.Register [
‚ćĚ       'GET'  '/users'       'ListUsers'   ()
‚ćĚ       'GET'  '/users/{id}'  'GetUser'     ()
‚ćĚ       'POST' '/users'       'CreateUser'  opts   ‚ćĚ opts is a namespace with metadata
‚ćĚ   ]
‚ćĚ   ‚ćĚ Namespace vector mode (.method .path .handler, and optionally .spec):
‚ćĚ   router.Register (
‚ćĚ       (method: 'GET'  ‚čĄ path: '/users'      ‚čĄ handler: 'ListUsers')
‚ćĚ       (method: 'GET'  ‚čĄ path: '/users/{id}' ‚čĄ handler: 'GetUser')
‚ćĚ       (method: 'POST' ‚čĄ path: '/users'      ‚čĄ handler: 'CreateUser' ‚čĄ spec: opts)
‚ćĚ   )
‚ćĚ   router.Start 8080

