    :Field Public  Info          ‚ćĚ namespace with title, version, description for OpenAPI info
    :Field Public  Debug‚Üź0       ‚ćĚ 0=all errors trapped, 1=stop on error in dispatch, 2=stop before user handler, 4=Jarvis framework debug, 8=Conga event logging, 16=stop before response, 32=Stark framework debug, 64=stop before routing
    :Field Public  OnErrorFn‚Üź''  ‚ćĚ if set, called as err OnErrorFn req after Fail 500 instead of resignalling; err is a ‚éēDMX clone
    :Field Private _routes       ‚ćĚ vector of route descriptor namespaces
    :Field Private _jarvis       ‚ćĚ underlying Jarvis instance

