    ‚ąá r‚ÜźRegister routes
      :Access Public
      ‚ćĚ Matrix mode:   N√ó4 matrix of (method path handler spec)
      ‚ćĚ Namespace mode: vector of namespaces, each with .method .path .handler and optionally .spec
      :If 2=‚ćī‚ćīroutes
        :If _routes[;2]{0‚ČĘ‚ČĘ‚äÉ‚ą©/{_NormalizePath¬®‚ćĶ}¬®‚ćļ ‚ćĶ}routes[;2]
            ‚éēSIGNAL ‚äā('EN' 11)('Message' ('STARK: Duplicate routes detected'))
        :EndIf
        routes[;2]‚Üź,¬®routes[;2]
        _routes‚ć™‚Üź4‚ÜĎ[2]routes,()
      :Else
        :For ns :In ,routes
          :If 9=ns.‚éēNC'spec'
              _Register ns.method ns.path (ns.handler ns.spec)
          :Else
              _Register ns.method ns.path ns.handler
          :EndIf
        :EndFor
      :EndIf
      r‚Üź_routes
