    ‚ąá

    stopIf‚Üź{1‚ąä‚ćĶ:-‚éēTRAP‚Üź0 'C' '‚éē‚Üź''Stopped for debugging... (Press Ctrl-Enter)''' ‚čĄ shy‚Üź0}

    ‚ćĚ pattern pathMatch path ‚Üí (matched pathParams)
    pathMatch‚Üź{
        patSplit pathSplit‚Üź'/'(‚Č†‚äÜ‚äĘ)¬®‚ćļ ‚ćĶ
        pathSplit‚ČĘ‚ć•‚ČĘpatSplit:0()
        varMask‚Üź'{'=‚äÉ¬®patSplit
        ‚ČĘ/(‚äā~varMask)/¬®patSplit pathSplit:0()
        names‚Üź({1‚Üď¬Į1‚Üď‚ćĶ}¬®patSplit[‚ćłvarMask])
        1(()‚éēVSET‚Üď‚ćČ‚ÜĎnames(pathSplit[‚ćłvarMask]))
    }

    ‚ćĚ Route an incoming Jarvis request to the matching handler
    ‚ąá result‚Üź_Dispatch req;routes;r;matched;pp;m;err
      :Access Public Instance
      stopIf DebugLevel 64                          ‚ćĚ stop before routing
      routes‚Üź(_routes[;1] ‚ąä‚ć•‚éēC ‚äāreq.Method)‚ĆŅ_routes
      :If 0=‚ČĘroutes
          req.Fail 404
          result‚Üź(
            detail: 'Not Found'
          )
          :Return
      :EndIf
      m pp‚Üź{(‚äÉ‚ćĶ) (‚ćĶ‚äÉ‚ćõ/2‚äÉ‚ćĶ)}‚Üď‚ćČ‚ÜĎroutes[;2] pathMatch¬®‚äāreq.Endpoint
      r‚Üźm‚ĆŅroutes
      :If 1‚Č†‚ČĘpp
          req.Fail 404
          result‚Üź(
            detail: 'Not Found'
          )
          :Return
      :EndIf
      r‚Üźr[1;]
      req.PathParams‚Üź‚äÉpp ‚ćĚ Shouldn't have multiple matches.
      req.QueryParams‚Üź() ‚éēVSET ‚Üďreq.QueryParams
      :If '_'=‚äÉ3‚äÉr
          result‚Üź(‚ćé3‚äÉr)req          ‚ćĚ internal handler (on Stark)
      :Else
          :If DebugLevel 32
              ‚éē‚Üź'STARK: ',req.Method,' ',req.Endpoint,' ‚Üí ',3‚äÉr
          :EndIf
          stopIf DebugLevel 2              ‚ćĚ stop before user handler
          :Trap 0 DebugLevel 1             ‚ćĚ disable trap if bit 1 set (stop on error)
              result‚Üź(Handlers‚ćé3‚äÉr)req
          :Else
              :If ~0‚ąä‚ćīOnErrorFn
                  err‚Üź()‚éēNS ‚éēDMX          ‚ćĚ deep clone ‚éēDMX before req.Fail may alter it
                  req.Fail 500
                  result‚Üźerr(Handlers‚ćéOnErrorFn)req
              :Else
                  ‚éēSIGNAL‚äā‚éēDMX.(('EN'EN)('EM'EM)('Message'(OSError{‚ćĶ,2‚ĆĹ(√ó‚ČĘ‚äÉ‚ć¨‚ćī2‚ĆĹ‚ćļ,‚äā'')/'") ("',‚äÉ‚ć¨‚ćī2‚ĆĹ‚ćļ}Message))) ‚ćĚ RESIGNAL
