    ‚ąá spec‚Üź_BuildOpenAPI;paths;r;pathKey;pathNS;method;op;opts;segs;varMask;param;pNS;ct;code;schemaNS;e;respNS;respKey;ctKey
      :Access Private Instance
      ‚ćĚ _Mangle mangles strings into valid APL names; ‚éēJSON will unmangle them
      spec‚Üź(
        openapi: '3.0.3'
        info: Info
      )
      ctKey‚Üź_Mangle'application/json'

      paths‚Üź()
      :For r :In ‚Üď_routes
          :If '_'=‚äÉ3‚äÉr ‚čĄ :Continue ‚čĄ :EndIf   ‚ćĚ skip internal routes

          ‚ćĚ Get or create path object
          pathKey‚Üź_Mangle 2‚äÉr
          :If 0=paths.‚éēNC‚äāpathKey
              paths ‚éēVSET ‚äāpathKey ()
          :EndIf
          pathNS‚Üźpaths ‚éēVGET pathKey

          ‚ćĚ Build operation object
          method‚Üź‚éēC 1‚äÉr
          op‚Üź(
            parameters: ‚ć¨
            responses: ()
          )

          ‚ćĚ Map metadata from route options
          opts‚Üź4‚äÉr
          op.operationId‚Üź3‚äÉr

          ‚ćĚ Extract path parameters from {param} segments
          ‚ćĚ If opts.params.{name} exists, its schema overrides the default 'string'
          segs‚Üź'/'(‚Č†‚äÜ‚äĘ)2‚äÉr
          varMask‚Üź'{'=‚äÉ¬®segs
          :For param :In {1‚Üď¬Į1‚Üď‚ćĶ}¬®varMask/segs
              :If 9=‚éēNC'opts' ‚čĄ :AndIf 9=opts.‚éēNC'params' ‚čĄ :AndIf 9=opts.params.‚éēNC‚äāparam
                  pNS‚Üź(name: param ‚čĄ in: 'path' ‚čĄ required: (‚äā'true') ‚čĄ schema: (opts.params‚ćéparam))
              :Else
                  pNS‚Üź(name: param ‚čĄ in: 'path' ‚čĄ required: (‚äā'true') ‚čĄ schema: (type: 'string'))
              :EndIf
              op.parameters,‚Üź‚äāpNS
          :EndFor
          :If 9=‚éēNC'opts'
              :If 2=opts.‚éēNC'operationId'  ‚čĄ op.operationId‚Üźopts.operationId  ‚čĄ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éēNC'summary'      ‚čĄ op.summary‚Üźopts.summary          ‚čĄ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éēNC'description'  ‚čĄ op.description‚Üźopts.description  ‚čĄ :EndIf
              :If 2‚Č§opts.‚éēNC'parameters'   ‚čĄ op.parameters,‚Üźopts.parameters   ‚čĄ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éēNC'tags'
                :If 2=‚Č°opts.tags
                  op.tags‚Üźopts.tags
                :Else
                  ‚éēSIGNAL ‚äā'tags must be a vector of character vectors. Depth 2'
                :EndIf
              :EndIf
              

              ‚ćĚ Request body schema
              :If 9=opts.‚éēNC'body'
                  ct‚Üź() ‚éēVSET ‚äāctKey (schema: opts.body)
                  op.requestBody‚Üź(required: (‚äā'true') ‚čĄ content: ct)
              :EndIf

              ‚ćĚ Success response: (statusCode schema)
              :If 2‚Č§opts.‚éēNC'response'
                  (code schemaNS)‚Üźopts.response
                  ct‚Üź() ‚éēVSET ‚äāctKey (schema: schemaNS)
                  respNS‚Üź(description: 'Successful response' ‚čĄ content: ct)
                  respKey‚Üź_Mangle‚ćēcode
                  op.responses ‚éēVSET ‚äārespKey respNS
              :EndIf

              ‚ćĚ Error responses: vector of (statusCode description) pairs
              :If 2‚Č§opts.‚éēNC'errors'
                  :For e :In opts.errors
                      respKey‚Üź_Mangle‚ćē‚äÉe
                      op.responses ‚éēVSET ‚äārespKey (description: 2‚äÉe)
                  :EndFor
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
          :If 0=‚ČĘop.parameters ‚čĄ op.‚éēEX'parameters' ‚čĄ :EndIf

          ‚ćĚ Default 200 response if none specified
          :If 0=‚ČĘop.responses.‚éēNL ¬Į2 ¬Į9
              respKey‚Üź_Mangle'200'
              op.responses ‚éēVSET ‚äārespKey (description: 'Successful response')
          :EndIf

          pathNS ‚éēVSET ‚äāmethod op
      :EndFor

      spec.paths‚Üźpaths
